OL,5,Cwoman refused rides
OL,6, Uber has been ordered to pay $1.1m
OL,7, (#795,000) to a blind woman who was
OL,8, refused rides on 14 occasions.
OL,10,FLisa Irving said on some occasions,
OL,11,Fdrivers were verbally abusive, or
OL,12,Fharassed her about transporting her
OL,13,Fguide dog, Bernie, in the car.
OL,15,FOne driver allegedly cut her trip short
OL,16,Fafter falsely claiming to have arrived
OL,17,Fat her destination.
OL,19,FAn independent arbitrator ruled Uber's
OL,20,Fdrivers had illegally discriminated
OL,21,Fagainst her due to her condition.
